### Test Tour Package API

# Available Status Values: ACTIVE, INACTIVE

# Get All Tour Packages (Public - No Auth Required)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/tour-packages

###

# Get Tour Package by ID (Public - No Auth Required)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/tour-packages/TOUR_PACKAGE_ID_HERE

###

